   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>CHAPTER ONE GOD'S ECONOMY AND MAN'S FAILURE Scripture Reading: 1 John 3:24; 4:13; Gen 1:26-27; 2:7; 1 Thes 5:23; 2 Cor 5:17; Gal 6:15; Gen 13:16; 15:5; Rev 12:5, 11; 14:1-5; Gen 6:3a; 11:4-9; Jer 2:13; 11:10; 2 Cor 13:14; 1 John 3:8; Matt 16:24; 1 John 2:15; Gal 1:4; 6:14; Rev 11:15 OUTLINE God's economy: To be one with man 1 John 3:24; 4:13: Creating man in His image Gen 1:26-27.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>Making man of three parts body, soul, and spirit Gen 2:7; 1 Thes 5:23.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>To make man His organism: To be man's life and content.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>To express Himself in humanity.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>To have a new creation out of His old creation 2 Cor 5:17; Gal 6:15: To impart Himself into His old creation.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>To consummate this project in four ages in the old creation and through four peoples of His old creation: In the age before law through the race of Adam.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>In the age of law through the earthly descendants of the race of Abraham Gen 13:16.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>In the age of grace through the heavenly descendants of the race of Abraham Gen 15:5.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>In the age of the kingdom through the overcomers of the races of Adam and of Abraham Rev 12:5, 11; 14:1-5.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>Man's failure: The failure of the race of Adam in the age before law: Becoming flesh at the time of the deluge Gen 6:3a.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>Becoming one with Satan at Babel Gen 11:4-9.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>The failure of the earthly descendants of the race of Abraham: Forsaking God with His old covenant Jer 2:13; 11:10b.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>Choosing Satan with his kingdom Jer 11:10a.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>The failure of the heavenly descendants of the race of Abraham: Defeated in the enjoyment of the processed Triune God cf.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>2 Cor 13:14.</S>
   <S PAR='16' RSNT='1' SNO='16'>Corrupted by Satan through sin, self, the world, and the religious world 1 John 3:8; Matt 16:24; 1 John 2:15; Gal 1:4; 6:14.</S>
   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>Christ calling the overcomers out of the heavenly descendants of the race of Abraham for the age of the kingdom: To consummate God's economy.</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>To bring in the kingdom of Christ and of God Rev 11:15.</S>
   </TEXT>
